file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.2
info:
  contact:
    name: FED API Support
    url: https://github.com/moov-io/fed
  description: FED API is designed to create FEDACH and FEDWIRE dictionaries.  The
    FEDACH dictionary contains receiving depository financial institutions (RDFI’s)
    which are qualified to receive ACH entries.  The FEDWIRE dictionary contains receiving
    depository financial institutions (RDFI’s) which are qualified to receive WIRE
    entries.  This project implements a modern REST HTTP API for FEDACH Dictionary
    and FEDWIRE Dictionary.
  license:
    name: Apache 2.0
    url: http://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0.html
  title: FED API
  version: v1
servers:
- description: Local development
  url: http://localhost:8086
tags:
- description: FEDACH Dictionary and FEDWIRE Dictionary
  name: FED
paths:
  /ping:
    get:
      operationId: ping
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            text/plain:
              example: PONG
          description: Service is running properly
      summary: Ping the FED service to check if running
      tags:
      - FED
  /fed/ach/search:
    get:
      operationId: searchFEDACH
      parameters:
      - description: Optional Request ID allows application developer to trace requests
          through the systems logs
        example: rs4f9915
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: X-Request-ID
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: Optional User ID used to perform this search
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: X-User-ID
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: FEDACH Financial Institution Name
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: name
        required: false
        schema:
          example: Farmers
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: FEDACH Routing Number for a Financial Institution
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: routingNumber
        required: false
        schema:
          example: "44112187"
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: FEDACH Financial Institution State
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: state
        required: false
        schema:
          example: OH
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: FEDACH Financial Institution City
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: city
        required: false
        schema:
          example: CALDWELL
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: FEDACH Financial Institution Postal Code
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: postalCode
        required: false
        schema:
          example: "43724"
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Maximum results returned by a search
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: limit
        required: false
        schema:
          example: 499
          type: integer
        style: form
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/ACHDictionary'
          description: FEDACH Participants returned from a search
        400:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
          description: Invalid, check error(s).
        500:
          description: Internal error, check error(s) and report the issue.
      summary: Search FEDACH names and metadata
      tags:
      - FED
  /fed/wire/search:
    get:
      operationId: searchFEDWIRE
      parameters:
      - description: Optional Request ID allows application developer to trace requests
          through the systems logs
        example: rs4f9915
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: X-Request-ID
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: Optional User ID used to perform this search
        explode: false
        in: header
        name: X-User-ID
        required: false
        schema:
          type: string
        style: simple
      - description: FEDWIRE Financial Institution Name
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: name
        required: false
        schema:
          example: MIDWEST
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: FEDWIRE Routing Number for a Financial Institution
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: routingNumber
        required: false
        schema:
          example: "91905114"
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: FEDWIRE Financial Institution State
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: state
        required: false
        schema:
          example: IA
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: FEDWIRE Financial Institution City
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: city
        required: false
        schema:
          example: IOWA CITY
          type: string
        style: form
      - description: Maximum results returned by a search
        explode: true
        in: query
        name: limit
        required: false
        schema:
          example: 499
          type: integer
        style: form
      responses:
        200:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/WIREDictionary'
          description: FEDWIRE Participants returned from a search
        400:
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/Error'
          description: Invalid, check error(s).
        500:
          description: Internal error, check error(s) and report the issue.
      summary: Search FEDWIRE names and metadata
      tags:
      - FED
components:
  schemas:
    ACHDictionary:
      description: Search results containing ACHDictionary of Participants
      example:
        ACHParticipants:
        - officeCode: O
          servicingFRBNumber: "041000014"
          viewCode: "1"
          customerName: FARMERS & MERCHANTS BANK
          cleanName: Chase
          routingNumber: "044112187"
          phoneNumber: "7407325621"
          logo:
            name: Chase
            url: https://logo.clearbit.com/chase.com
          newRoutingNumber: "000000000"
          recordTypeCode: "1"
          revised: "20190311"
          achLocation:
            postalExtension: "0000"
            address: 430 NORTH ST
            city: CALDWELL
            postalCode: "43724"
            state: OH
          statusCode: "1"
        - officeCode: O
          servicingFRBNumber: "041000014"
          viewCode: "1"
          customerName: FARMERS & MERCHANTS BANK
          cleanName: Chase
          routingNumber: "044112187"
          phoneNumber: "7407325621"
          logo:
            name: Chase
            url: https://logo.clearbit.com/chase.com
          newRoutingNumber: "000000000"
          recordTypeCode: "1"
          revised: "20190311"
          achLocation:
            postalExtension: "0000"
            address: 430 NORTH ST
            city: CALDWELL
            postalCode: "43724"
            state: OH
          statusCode: "1"
      properties:
        ACHParticipants:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/ACHParticipant'
          type: array
    ACHParticipant:
      description: ACHParticipant holds a FedACH dir routing record as defined by
        Fed ACH Format.  https://www.frbservices.org/EPaymentsDirectory/achFormat.html
      example:
        officeCode: O
        servicingFRBNumber: "041000014"
        viewCode: "1"
        customerName: FARMERS & MERCHANTS BANK
        cleanName: Chase
        routingNumber: "044112187"
        phoneNumber: "7407325621"
        logo:
          name: Chase
          url: https://logo.clearbit.com/chase.com
        newRoutingNumber: "000000000"
        recordTypeCode: "1"
        revised: "20190311"
        achLocation:
          postalExtension: "0000"
          address: 430 NORTH ST
          city: CALDWELL
          postalCode: "43724"
          state: OH
        statusCode: "1"
      properties:
        routingNumber:
          description: The institution's routing number
          example: "044112187"
          maxLength: 9
          minLength: 9
          type: string
        officeCode:
          description: |
            Main/Head Office or Branch

            * `O` - Main
            * `B` - Branch
          enum:
          - O
          - B
          example: O
          maxLength: 1
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        servicingFRBNumber:
          description: Servicing Fed's main office routing number
          example: "041000014"
          maxLength: 9
          minLength: 9
          type: string
        recordTypeCode:
          description: |
            The code indicating the ABA number to be used to route or send ACH items to the RDFI

            * `0` - Institution is a Federal Reserve Bank
            * `1` - Send items to customer routing number
            * `2` - Send items to customer using new routing number field
          enum:
          - "0"
          - "1"
          - "2"
          example: "1"
          maxLength: 1
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        revised:
          description: |
            Date of last revision

            * YYYYMMDD
            * Blank
          example: "20190311"
          maxLength: 8
          type: string
        newRoutingNumber:
          description: Financial Institution's new routing number resulting from a
            merger or renumber
          example: "000000000"
          maxLength: 9
          minLength: 9
          type: string
        customerName:
          description: Financial Institution Name
          example: FARMERS & MERCHANTS BANK
          maxLength: 36
          type: string
        achLocation:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/ACHLocation'
        phoneNumber:
          description: The Financial Institution's phone number
          example: "7407325621"
          maxLength: 10
          minLength: 10
          type: string
        statusCode:
          description: |
            Code is based on the customers receiver code

            * `1` - Receives Gov/Comm
          enum:
          - "1"
          example: "1"
          maxLength: 1
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        viewCode:
          description: |-
            Code is current view

            * `1` - Current view
          enum:
          - "1"
          example: "1"
          maxLength: 1
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        cleanName:
          description: Normalized name of ACH participant
          example: Chase
          type: string
        logo:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Logo'
    ACHLocation:
      description: ACHLocation is the FEDACH delivery address
      example:
        postalExtension: "0000"
        address: 430 NORTH ST
        city: CALDWELL
        postalCode: "43724"
        state: OH
      properties:
        address:
          description: Street Address
          example: 430 NORTH ST
          maxLength: 36
          type: string
        city:
          description: City
          example: CALDWELL
          maxLength: 20
          type: string
        state:
          description: State
          example: OH
          maxLength: 2
          minLength: 2
          type: string
        postalCode:
          description: Postal Code
          example: "43724"
          maxLength: 5
          minLength: 5
          type: string
        postalExtension:
          description: Postal Code Extension
          example: "0000"
          maxLength: 4
          minLength: 4
          type: string
    WIREDictionary:
      description: Search results containing WIREDictionary of Participants
      example:
        WIREParticipants:
        - date: "20190401"
          cleanName: Chase
          routingNumber: "091905114"
          wireLocation:
            city: IOWA CITY
            state: IA
          fundsTransferStatus: Y
          fundsSettlementOnlyStatus: S
          telegraphicName: MIDWESTONE B&T
          logo:
            name: Chase
            url: https://logo.clearbit.com/chase.com
          customerName: MIDWESTONE BK
          bookEntrySecuritiesTransferStatus: N
        - date: "20190401"
          cleanName: Chase
          routingNumber: "091905114"
          wireLocation:
            city: IOWA CITY
            state: IA
          fundsTransferStatus: Y
          fundsSettlementOnlyStatus: S
          telegraphicName: MIDWESTONE B&T
          logo:
            name: Chase
            url: https://logo.clearbit.com/chase.com
          customerName: MIDWESTONE BK
          bookEntrySecuritiesTransferStatus: N
      properties:
        WIREParticipants:
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/WIREParticipant'
          type: array
    WIREParticipant:
      description: WIREParticipant holds a FedWIRE dir routing record as defined by
        Fed WIRE Format.  https://frbservices.org/EPaymentsDirectory/fedwireFormat.html
      example:
        date: "20190401"
        cleanName: Chase
        routingNumber: "091905114"
        wireLocation:
          city: IOWA CITY
          state: IA
        fundsTransferStatus: Y
        fundsSettlementOnlyStatus: S
        telegraphicName: MIDWESTONE B&T
        logo:
          name: Chase
          url: https://logo.clearbit.com/chase.com
        customerName: MIDWESTONE BK
        bookEntrySecuritiesTransferStatus: N
      properties:
        routingNumber:
          description: The institution's routing number
          example: "091905114"
          maxLength: 9
          minLength: 9
          type: string
        telegraphicName:
          description: Short name of financial institution
          example: MIDWESTONE B&T
          maxLength: 18
          type: string
        customerName:
          description: Financial Institution Name
          example: MIDWESTONE BK
          maxLength: 36
          type: string
        wireLocation:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/WIRELocation'
        fundsTransferStatus:
          description: |
            Designates funds transfer status

            * `Y` - Eligible
            * `N` - Ineligible
          enum:
          - Y
          - N
          example: Y
          maxLength: 1
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        fundsSettlementOnlyStatus:
          description: |
            Designates funds settlement only status

             * `S` - Settlement-Only
          enum:
          - S
          maxLength: 1
          type: string
        bookEntrySecuritiesTransferStatus:
          description: |
            Designates book entry securities transfer status

            * `Y` - Eligible
            * `N` - Ineligible
          enum:
          - Y
          - N
          example: N
          maxLength: 1
          minLength: 1
          type: string
        date:
          description: |
            Date of last revision

            * YYYYMMDD
            * Blank
          example: "20190401"
          maxLength: 8
          type: string
        cleanName:
          description: Normalized name of Wire participant
          example: Chase
          type: string
        logo:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Logo'
    WIRELocation:
      description: WIRELocation is the FEDWIRE delivery address
      example:
        city: IOWA CITY
        state: IA
      properties:
        city:
          description: City
          example: IOWA CITY
          maxLength: 25
          type: string
        state:
          description: State
          example: IA
          maxLength: 2
          minLength: 2
          type: string
    Logo:
      description: Company logo of the Fed ACH or Wire participant
      example:
        name: Chase
        url: https://logo.clearbit.com/chase.com
      properties:
        name:
          description: Company name
          example: Chase
          type: string
        url:
          description: URL to the company logo
          example: https://logo.clearbit.com/chase.com
          type: string
    Error:
      properties:
        error:
          description: An error message describing the problem intended for humans.
          example: Example error, see description
          type: string
      required:
      - error
